    "We propagated NQ from GAMA; -GAMA-G15Deep (Kafle et al. 2018; Driver et al.",
    "2022): galaxies were selected with input redshift quality Z_QUAL ≥ 3 and with redshifts z > 0.001 to avoid stellar contamination.We assigned NQ = Z_QUAL; -G10-COSMOS (Davies et al. 2015): galaxies were selected with Z_BEST as the redshift value, and otherwise following the documentation for selecting galaxy redshifts: Z_BEST > 0.0001, Z_USE < 3, and STAR_GALAXY_CLASS = 0.",
